.DT
hide
$MUDNAME$ player help
hide

.SH hide - Used to hide in dark places
.SI 5
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
hide
hide stop
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Hide is used to hide in the shadows in a room.  The difficulty of the command is based on
your skill, and the amount of light in the room and on you.

You cannot hide while you are fighting.

You will stop hiding after a period of time, if you are spotted, or if
you use hide stop.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
>hide
You find a place to hide.

>hide stop
You stop trying to hide.

>hide
You can't seem to find a suitable place to hide.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
sneak
.EP
